A GOGO has been charged with murdering her husband by allegedly stabbing him. The gogo from Florida, USA, reportedly stabbed him more than 140 times inside the kitchen of their home. The New York Post reports that 62-year-old Melvin Weller was found by his 41-year-old stepson, lying in a pool of blood in his Palm Springs residence on 11 February. The stepson called the cops, who later found multiple knives and a meat chopper in the sink. According to the publication, gogo Joan Burke (61) was lying in bed and did not say a word when cops showed up. Following an investigation into the fatal stabbing, she was hospitalised and later arrested. An autopsy revealed that the madala had been stabbed over 140 times. He also had a skull fracture from being hit in the head with a meat chopper. The gogo has been charged with first-degree murder.